ss, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a kind of tailed ape</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0525.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:23:5s\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Paus.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.23.5s</biblScope> </bibl>q., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0545.tlg001:16:21\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ael.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ NA\">NA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.21</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"b\" id=\"n93435.3\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> a fabulous people in Ethiopia, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0060.tlg001.perseus-grc3:1:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.S.\">D.S.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.18</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n93435.4\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ἡ ἔντασις</ref></xr>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl> </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n93435.5\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in pl., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a play in which the Chorus consisted of Satyrs, Satyric drama</tr_>, forming the fourth piece of a Tragic tetralogy, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὅταν Σατύρους ποιῇς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg008.perseus-grc1:157\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">157</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ποηταὶ σατύρων</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ T